  "keyFeatures": [
    "Fine-tune encoder (GLiNER) and decoder (LLM) models with LoRA or full fine-tuning",
    "Adaptive Inference — automatically retrains models on live production data",
    "OpenAI- and Anthropic-compatible API endpoints for drop-in integration",
    "Synthetic data generation for NER, classification, and decoder tasks",
    "On-demand and serverless inference with dedicated GPU deployments",
    "Dataset management, evaluation, and model checkpointing",
    "Agent Skills — give AI coding agents (Cursor, Claude Code) full Pioneer API knowledge",
    "Projects and deployments for organizing production model endpoints"
